1293.3 points, while the all industrials index rose 14.0 points to
3450.9 points.
</P>
<P>
BHP added ten cents to 15.92 Australian dollars. CRA gained
four cents to 18.12 Australian dollars. News Corp climbed three
cents to 6.58 Australian dollars.
</P>
<P>
The national turnover totaled 226.4 million shares, worth 653.0
million Australian dollars (515.9 million US dollars).
</P>
<P>
On the Sydney Futures Exchange, the September share price index
contract rose 9.0 points to 2227.0 points.  
