Creative topped the gainers' list as it picked up by 1.8
Singapore dollars to finish at 7.75 Singapore dollars. Sime UEP
Prop was next, rising by 56 cents to 3.34 Singapore dollars, while
Cerebos was 40 cents higher at 11.7 Singapore dollars.
</P>
<P>
