declined by 70 cents to close at 26 Singapore dollars. The
Overseas Chinese Banking Corporation (OCBC) Foreign lost 40 cents
to end at 16.6 Singapore dollars, while the Singapore Airlines
Foreign fell by 30 cents to finish at 14.2 Singapore dollars.
