<HEADLINE> Tennis Star Kimiko Date to Retire Soon </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, September 24 (Xinhua) -- Japanese tennis star Kimiko
Date will retire at the end of the season, local reports said on
Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
