of the Ministry of the People's Armed Forces as saying that "a
training small submarine of a Korean People's Army unit, which
left Won San port on September 13 and engaged in a routine
training on the north's East Sea of Korean, might drift about with
an engine trouble and strike a rock on the sea off Kangrung."
</P>
<P>
