14 ever since the outbreak of the disease.
</P>
<P>
In Safdarjung hospital, the number of cases have shot up from
about 20 till Saturday to 92, while the number has almost doubled
in Kalawati Saran hospital in the city. Many other hospitals in
the capital have also reported cases of dengue fever.
</P>
