make electricity available to all regions, including the villages.
</P>
<P>
He said the electricity demand growth in entering the 21st
century will still be high due to rapid development in the
industrial sector.
</P>
<P>
In the year 2003/2004, he said, the installed capacity is
expected to reach more than 35,000 megawatts and the
electrification ratio is about 74 percent.  
